Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: The City of Senatobia is a thriving, bustling, growing community located only 30 minutes south of Memphis, Tennessee. As the seat of Tate County, Senatobia’s population includes approximately 7,000 people, while Tate County overall reports about 27,000.
